<para><bold>GLOverlayUI</bold> is a desktop application that demonstrates the integration of a real-time OpenGL rendering pipeline with a native wxWidgets GUI. It features an interactive 2D scene rendered on a <computeroutput>wxGLCanvas</computeroutput>, including a clickable OpenGL overlay and a dynamic control panel using native UI widgets.</para>
<para><hruler/>
 </para>
