</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>ğŸ“Œ Toggleable right-side control panel with:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>wxSlider</computeroutput> to control object scale</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><computeroutput>wxCheckBox</computeroutput> to toggle visibility of scene objects</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>ğŸ§¼ Clean separation between rendering engine and UI logic</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>ğŸ” Real-time interaction between OpenGL scene and native UI</para>
